The paper deals with the task of multi-human 3D pose estimation from multiple calibrated camera views, which is a classic problem in computer vision. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a novel solution that involves multi-human tracking, which falls under the category of cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also mentions the use of deep learning techniques, which is a common theme in cs.MM (Multimedia). The paper also discusses the efficiency of the proposed method, which could fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
